How to play:
    How to move paddles:
        Use keys 'w' to move pink paddle up and 's' to move it down.
        Use keys 'up arrow' and 'down arrow' to move orange paddle.
    How to start game:
        After each goal, press 'Press to Play' to continue game.
        To reset the score press 'Press to Start New Game'.

References:
GfG. (2023, February 15). Pong game in JavaScript. GeeksforGeeks. https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/pong-game-in-javascript/ 